en. Proponowany podzia\u0142 to 60% na obni\u017cenie cen i 40% na zwi\u0119kszenie wydatk\u00f3w na reklamy.<\/li>\n<li><b>Analiza studi\u00f3w przypadk\u00f3w<\/b>: Zainspiruj si\u0119 sukcesami innych, jak w przypadku Zulle Kitchen, kt\u00f3re udowodni\u0142o, \u017ce pocz\u0105tkowe straty zwi\u0105zane z obni\u017caniem cen mog\u0105 prowadzi\u0107 do znacznych zysk\u00f3w w d\u0142u\u017cszym okresie.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, skoncentruj si\u0119 na obni\u017caniu cen, aby zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 sprzeda\u017c, a je\u015bli Twoje wyniki to wspieraj\u0105, rozwa\u017c zwi\u0119kszenie wydatk\u00f3w na reklamy.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zdoby\u0107 udzia\u0142 w rynku w bran\u017cy Beauty i FMCG?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak skutecznie zw<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6706,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6705","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6705"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6705"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6705\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6706"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6705"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"cate